<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8"/>
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge"/>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1"/>
    <meta name="description" content=""/>
    <meta name="author" content=""/>
    <title>Gage Talk</title>
    <!-- stylesheet-->
    <!-- jquery-->
    <script src="javascripts/angular.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/jquery-ui.min.css"/>
    <!-- bootstrap-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="bootstrap/css/bootstrap-theme.min.css"/>
    <!--<link rel="stylesheet/less" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/style.less">
    -->
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
    <nav role="navigation" class="navbar navbar-default">
        <!-- Brand and toggle get grouped for better mobile display-->
        <div class="navbar-header">
            <button type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-ex1-collapse" class="navbar-toggle"><span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span>
                <span class="icon-bar"></span></button><a href="/" class="navbar-brand"><%=title%></a>
        </div>
        <!-- Collect the nav links, forms, and other content for toggling-->
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse navbar-right navbar-ex1-collapse">
            <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
                <li class="active"><a href="/"><%=subtitle1%></a></li>
                <li><a href="/owner_manage"><%=subtitle2%></a></li>
                <li><a href="/customer_manage"><%=subtitle3%></a></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        <!-- /.navbar-collapse-->
    </nav>
    <div id="content">
        <div id="login">
            <h2>로그인 해주세요.</h2>
            <p>관리자 페이지를 이용하시려면 로그인을 해주셔야 합니다.</p>
            <form action="/checklogin" method="post">
                <div class="input-group"><span class="input-group-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-user"></span></span>
                    <input name="id" type="text" placeholder="아이디" class="form-control"/>
                </div><br/>
                <div class="input-group"><span class="input-group-addon"><span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock"></span></span>
                    <input name="password" type="password" placeholder="암 호" class="form-control"/>
                </div><br/>
                <button type="submit" aria-label="Left Align" class="btn btn-default"><span aria-hidden="true" class="glyphicon glyphicon-triangle-right">로그인</span></button>
            </form>
        </div>
        <div id="logged_in">
            <h2>로그인 되었습니다.</h2>
            <p>이제 다른 페이지를 이용하실 수 있습니다.</p>
            <p><a href="/checklogin/logout" role="button" class="btn btn-warning">로그아웃</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
<script src="javascripts_lib/less.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
<script src="javascripts_lib/jquery-1.11.2.min.js"></script>
